      "step_text": "Pop a piece of fruit with your breakfast and tuck a colourful side salad or some steamed veg alongside your evening meal."
    },
    {
      "kr_id": 20,
      "step_text": "Fill a reusable water bottle in the morning and keep it close so you can sip from it throughout the day."
    },
    {
      "kr_id": 21,
      "step_text": "Swap one processed snack for a simple homemade option like chopped veg with hummus or a small handful of nuts."
    },
    {
      "kr_id": 22,
      "step_text": "Include a protein at each main meal, for example eggs at breakfast, beans or chicken at lunch and yoghurt or fish at dinner."
    }
  ]
}

