      "kr_id": 56,
      "step_text": "Prepare a clear container of washed, ready-to-grab fruit and vegetables and place it at eye level in the fridge so it’s the first thing you see."
    },
    {
      "kr_id": 57,
      "step_text": "Choose a single refillable water bottle and keep it filled in the fridge or on your desk in plain sight so there’s one easy option to pick up."
    },
